<!--########################################################--> <!--### Phonebook & Firmware Settings ###--> <!--########################################################-->

<!--# Codec Order --> <codec_priority_list idx="1">%%codec1%%,%%codec2%%,%%codec3%%,%%codec4%%</codec_priority_list> <!--# Codec Size --> <codec_size idx="1">20</codec_size> <!--# sRTP Setting URS--> <user_srtp idx="1">disabled</user_srtp> <!--# sRTP Setting SRV--> <srv_srtp_auth idx="1">off</srv_srtp_auth> <!--# DTMF Method --> <user_dtmf_info idx="1">off</user_dtmf_info> <!--# Full SDP Answer --> <user_full_sdp_answer idx="1">on</user_full_sdp_answer>

<!--######################### LAN #########################--> {IF network=LOCALLAN}
<!--# STUN Server Default Setting #--> <stun_server></stun_server> <stun_binding_interval>30</stun_binding_interval> <keepalive_interval idx="1">off</keepalive_interval> <srv_sip_ua_data_server_nat_adaption idx="1">disabled</srv_sip_ua_data_server_nat_adaption>
<!--# IP Adress of the 3CX PhoneSystem to register to (SIP) #--> <user_host idx="1">%%pbx_ip%%:%%param::sipport%%</user_host>

<!--# SPM Default Setting #--> <user_outbound idx="1">%%pbx_ip%%:%%param::sipport%%</user_outbound>
<!--# Provisioning Update Link #--> <setting_server>%%PROVLINKLOCAL%%/cfg{mac}</setting_server>
<!--# Registraion and Subscribtion timerouts/renewal #--> <user_expiry idx="1">120</user_expiry>
<!--# Rport and Received handing for invalid NAT configuration #--> <enable_rport_rfc3581>on</enable_rport_rfc3581> {ENDIF}
<!--######################### STUN #########################--> {IF network=REMOTESTUN} <!--# IP Adress of the 3CX PhoneSystem to register to (SIP) #--> <!--# The "user_host" field contains the ip address and SIP port of the SIP Registrar and Proxy - in this case 3CXPS. The "pbx_ip" and "param::sipport" variables will be replaced by the IP Address and SIP Port of 3CXPS.--> <user_host idx="1">%%pbx_ip%%:%%param::sipport%%</user_host>

By default this field is left blank so the phone can select a port at random.--> <sip_use_different_ports>off</sip_use_different_ports> <network_id_port>%%phonesipport%%</network_id_port>
<!--# Audio Default Port Range (SDP/RTP) #--> <rtp_port_start>%%rtp_port_min%%</rtp_port_start> <rtp_port_end>%%rtp_port_max%%</rtp_port_end>

<!--# Rport and Received handing for invalid NAT configuration #--> <enable_rport_rfc3581>on</enable_rport_rfc3581> {ENDIF}
